node.text:
Greek boutique hotel 🤍 #archoskar
The 'KÁLESMA'.
Designed by K-STUDIO (@k_studio_gr, 2020).
Located in Mykonos, Greece.
Photos by Yiorgos Kordakis (@yiorgoskordakis).
Description by K-STUDIO.
.
"The family is one of nature's masterpieces." — George Santayana. #architectureoskar
.
'KÁLESMA' is not really a hotel. It is a village, in the traditional Mykonian sense. There is a local saying, that when a couple marry they make a village, meaning that they will build a home that will grow, over the years, to accommodate generation after generation of their family. 'KÁLESMA' reimagines the concept of the extended family home, as an intimate hospitality destination that invites guests to connect to the essence of Cycladic life.
.
#mykonos #greek #boutique #hotel

node.text:
Family home facing the ocean ✨ #archoskar
The 'Two Angle House'.
Designed by MEGOWAN (@megowanarchitectural, 2018).
Located in Mount Eliza, Victoria, Australia.
Photos by Tom Blachford (@blachford).
Description by MEGOWAN.
.
"Individually, we are one drop. Together, we are an ocean." — Ryunosuke Satoro. #architectureoskar
.
Located in the seaside town of Mount Eliza in Victoria, Australia, is about contrast. The interior and exterior are a play on the contrast between two angles of internal organization, the contrast between warm and cold materials and a considered contrast between architecture and landscape.
.
#ocean #victoria #contrast #angle

node.text:
"Probably the most famous opera house in the world" ✨ #archoskar
The 'Opéra Garnier' ('Palais Garnier').
Designed by Charles Garnier (1861-1875).
Located in Place de l'Opéra, 9th arrondissement, Paris, France.
Photo by Fabien (@petit.yogi, 2019).
.
"I call architecture frozen music." — Johann Wolfgang von Goethe. #architectureoskar
.
It was built for the Paris Opera from 1861 to 1875 at the behest of Emperor Napoleon III. Initially referred to as le nouvel Opéra de Paris (the new Paris Opera), it soon became known as the Palais Garnier, "in acknowledgment of its extraordinary opulence" and the architect Charles Garnier's plans and designs, which are representative of the Napoleon III style.
.
#opera #paris #operahouse #garnier

node.text:
Private Bali villa 🌴 #archoskar
The 'House BK' (325 m²).
Designed by Caceres + Tous Studio (@caceres_tous_studio, 2018).
Located in Bali, Indonesia.
Photos by KIE (@kiearch).
.
"Architecture is the learned game, correct and magnificent, of forms assembled in the light." — Le Corbusier. #architectureoskar
.
The materials used on the house are mostly patterned concrete, wood and the vegetation and landscape as a third one. This combination makes the concrete more natural playing along with all the green and wood besides it. The concrete boxes disappear through the vegetation and landscape.
.
#bali #concrete #private #indonesia

node.text:
Family residence with high ceiling ✨ #archoskar
The 'House in Ourém' (410 m²).
Designed by Filipe Saraiva Arquitectos (@filipesaraivaarquitectos, 2016).
Located in Ourém, Portugal.
Photos by João Morgado (@joaodmorgado).
Description by Filipe Saraiva Arquitectos.
.
"Fashion is architecture: it is a matter of proportions." — Coco Chanel. #architectureoskar
.
The house is located on a piece of land in Ourém, characterized by its rectangular configuration, with a descending slope in the south direction (next to the public road). The difference in height between the highest point and the lowest point is approximately 4.50m. It is a farmland with a natural landscape, facing south and overlooking the Castle of Ourém.
.
#contemporary #ceiling #portugal #cocochanel

node.text:
Luxury jungle villa 🌴 #archoskar
The 'UMAN HA' (2515 m²).
Designed by Zepto Realty (@zeptorealty).
Visualized by UBICUOO (@ubicuoo.studio).
Expected to be located in Tulum, Mexico.
Description by Zepto Realty.
.
"Life is a zoo in a jungle." — Peter De Vries. #architectureoskar
.
'UMAN HA' is a three bedroom luxury jungle villa that despite having a modern character is proposed with local materials such as chukum. To give privacy to the spaces and cover the direct rays of the sun, we use natural wood from the region. Located in Tulum's newest living community, villa 'UMAN HA' is just a few minutes walk from the community's beach clubs and cenotes.
.
#luxury #jungle #tulum #mexico

node.text:
Brooklyn townhouse ✨ #archoskar
The 'Cobble Hill Townhouse'.
Designed by Workshop/APD (@workshopapd).
Located in Brooklyn, New York City, New York, USA.
Photos by Donna Dotan Photography (@donnadotanphoto).
Description by Workshop/APD.
.
"We shape our buildings; thereafter they shape us." — Winston Churchill. #architectureoskar
.
Nestled between two classic 1900s buildings on a leafy Brooklyn street, this ground-up townhouse embodies the ever-changing neighborhood’s energy with a forward-thinking design in Belgian brick, glass and steel. The family home features bright, comfortable rooms that take full advantage of the spacious lot’s light and views, a jaw-dropping chef’s kitchen, and a penthouse studio and terrace with a modern jacuzzi.
.
#brooklyn #newyorkcity #newyork #churchill
